org.openntf.todo.v1

Class UnitTestResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openntf.todo.v1.UnitTestResource

  • public class UnitTestResource
extends Object
    Author:
    Paul Withers Endpoints for unit testing. This does not interact with the backend database, just with dummy Java objects and converting to/from JSON. All endpoints check to ensure the DEBUG_KEY has been passed (see validateKey(HttpServletRequest).
